{
  "stem": "1550.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I mean, there was nothing-- So the Greek government, of course, did not want us there, because they-- Greek-- Greece is a small country.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They had enough trouble to fight the war against the big power like Italy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So they wanted to get rid of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So eventually-- eventually-- I don't know what went on behind the scenes-- somehow we got coal.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "One fine day, a barge arrived with coal, and it was loaded on to the ship and we sailed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We sailed east, in the easterly direction.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we sailed east, and-- of course the captain, in charge of the ship.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We sailed for about a day or two, and then the captain said, we have to go back, because we don't have enough coal.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We can't make it to Palestine, or not even to Cyprus or anywhere else.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There is not enough coal there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- but we didn't want to go back, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because we didn't want to go back to enemy country, because we were already on our way to Allied territory.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he said we had no coal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What happened was the ship came to a standstill.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The ship stopped in the middle of the ocean.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So what do you do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What we did was, our leadership-- most of these people in our leadership, or some of them, were Czech.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And one of them was a Czech Air Force officer who know, somehow-- who had a good idea on how to operate a ship.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So, in other words, we arrested the captain and he took over the ship, together with the first Greek-- with the First Officer, who was also a Greek, who decided to cooperate with us.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we continued.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "However, how do you continue when you have no coal?",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
